gend\r\n-----------\r\n |  - bar\r\n||  - double bar\r\n||o - repeat start\r\no|| - repeat end\r\n*|  - double bar (ending)\r\n :  - bar (freetime)\r\n $  - Segno\r\n &  - Coda\r\nTempo markers -  = BPM(8/16=s8/s16), where s8 = swing 8ths, s16 = swing 16ths",
